import React, { useState } from 'react' const RestaurantDetails = (props) => { let opHours=Object.entries(props.detail.operating_hours); console.log(opHours) return (<>

{props.detail.name}

{opHours.map((item)=>

{item[0]}-{item[1]}

)}

})}
) } export default RestaurantDetails
